      • register

        public V register(K key,
         V value,
         boolean update)
        Description copied from interface: Registry
        Registers a key-value pair. Both key and value must pass the validation tests. If the key was already registered, it will be returned. If the key was already registered, and update is true, the value will be replaced.
        Specified by:
